title: Whitesnake *LIVE* from London, UK
description:
David Coverdale heads up this head bangin' concert with the rest of the band and a "good time was had by all"! This 1 hour (approx) concert includes tunes from his days as the lead singer of Deep Purple and the hits from Whitesnake's hey day.

Songs include "Burn", "Ready An' Willing", "Is This Love?", "Give Me All Your Love", "Snake Dance", "Still of the Night", and more. 


This video was capped from HD-Net and upped for your viewing pleasure. This is from their Concert Series and we left the program opening and HD-Net logo in the opening sequence just to give it that "TV viewing" feel. Hope it fits.....
